answers.text:
We had a "generic" policy as follows:
at every intersection;
at a "significant" curve;
at a "significant" hill crest;
a light visible at all times in residential areas;
no more than 500 between lights in residential areas.
We also set wattage (lumens) specs for intersections, based on road categories.


